{"type":"message","id":"b67a5cbe","parentId":"8389a859","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:03.866Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，项目已经存在了。让我快速查看：\n1. 现有的低代码引擎代码\n2. 前端开发的参考文档\n3. 项目结构\n\n然后立即开始开发。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_23e82330ccbe460bbe993673","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/Tianyou.LowCode.Engine/FormEngine.cs"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3699aef649de45afb5c19394","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/06-前端开发.md","limit":200}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d5973ee8d61e4a9ebab710a7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3462,"output":148,"cacheRead":13632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17242,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774227298068}}
{"type":"message","id":"421ff70c","parentId":"b67a5cbe","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:03.990Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_23e82330ccbe460bbe993673","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using Tianyou.Core.Abstractions;\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.LowCode.Engine;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// 表单引擎 - 核心低代码引擎\n/// </summary>\npublic class FormEngine\n{\n    private readonly IMetadataRepository _metadataRepository;\n    private readonly IPluginManager _pluginManager;\n    private readonly IServiceProvider _serviceProvider;\n    \n    public FormEngine(\n        IMetadataRepository metadataRepository,\n        IPluginManager pluginManager,\n        IServiceProvider serviceProvider)\n    {\n        _metadataRepository = metadataRepository;\n        _pluginManager = pluginManager;\n        _serviceProvider = serviceProvider;\n    }\n    \n    /// <summary>\n    /// 加载表单\n    /// </summary>\n    public async Task<IFormInstance> LoadFormAsync(string formId, string? dataId = null)\n    {\n        var metadata = await _metadataRepository.GetFormMetadataAsync(formId);\n        if (metadata == null)\n        {\n            throw new FormNotFoundException($\"表单 {formId} 不存在\");\n        }\n        \n        var formInstance = new FormInstance(metadata, _serviceProvider);\n        \n        foreach (var pluginRef in metadata.Plugins)\n        {\n            var plugin = await _pluginManager.LoadPluginAsync<FormPluginBase>(pluginRef.PluginId);\n            if (plugin != null)\n            {\n                formInstance.RegisterPlugin(plugin);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(dataId))\n        {\n            var data = await _metadataRepository.LoadDataAsync(formId, dataId);\n            formInstance.Model.SetDataEntity(data);\n        }\n        else\n        {\n            var newData = CreateEmptyData(metadata);\n            formInstance.Model.SetDataEntity(newData);\n        }\n        \n        await formInstance.OnAfterBindDataAsync();\n        return formInstance;\n    }\n    \n    private DynamicObject CreateEmptyData(FormMetadata metadata)\n    {\n        var data = new DynamicObject { Id = Guid.NewGuid().ToString() };\n        \n        foreach (var field in metadata.Fields)\n        {\n            data[field.Code] = field.DefaultValue ?? GetDefaultValue(field.DataType);\n        }\n        \n        foreach (var entry in metadata.Entries)\n        {\n            data[entry.Code] = new List<DynamicObject>();\n        }\n        \n        return data;\n    }\n    \n    private object? GetDefaultValue(DataType dataType) => dataType switch\n    {\n        DataType.String => string.Empty,\n        DataType.Integer => 0,\n        DataType.Decimal => 0m,\n        DataType.Boolean => false,\n        _ => null\n    };\n    \n    public async Task<OperationResult> SaveFormAsync(IFormInstance formInstance)\n    {\n        var validationResult = await ValidateFormAsync(formInstance);\n        if (!validationResult.IsValid)\n        {\n            return OperationResult.Fail(string.Join(\"\\n\", validationResult.Errors.Select(e => e.Message)));\n        }\n        \n        await formInstance.OnBeforeOperationAsync(\"save\");\n        var data = formInstance.Model.GetDataEntity();\n        await _metadataRepository.SaveDataAsync(formInstance.FormId, data);\n        await formInstance.OnAfterOperationAsync(\"save\");\n        \n        return OperationResult.Ok(\"保存成功\");\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<ValidationResult> ValidateFormAsync(IFormInstance formInstance)\n    {\n        var result = ValidationResult.Success();\n        var metadata = formInstance.Metadata;\n        var data = formInstance.Model.GetDataEntity();\n        \n        foreach (var field in metadata.Fields)\n        {\n            if (field.Required)\n            {\n                var value = data.GetValue<object>(field.Code);\n                if (value == null || (value is string s && string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(s)))\n                {\n                    result.Errors.Add(new ValidationError\n                    {\n                        Field = field.Code,\n                        Message = $\"{field.Name}为必填项\"\n                    });\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        result.IsValid = result.Errors.Count == 0;\n        return result;\n    }\n}\n\npublic interface IFormInstance\n{\n    string FormId { get; }\n    FormMetadata Metadata { get; }\n    IFormView View { get; }\n    IDataModel Model { get; }\n    \n    void RegisterPlugin(FormPluginBase plugin);\n    Task OnAfterBindDataAsync();\n    Task OnBeforeOperationAsync(string operationKey);\n    Task OnAfterOperationAsync(string operationKey);\n}\n\npublic class FormInstance : IFormInstance\n{\n    private readonly FormMetadata _metadata;\n    private readonly FormView _view;\n    private readonly DataModel _model;\n    private readonly List<FormPluginBase> _plugins = new();\n    \n    public FormInstance(FormMetadata metadata, IServiceProvider serviceProvider)\n    {\n        _metadata = metadata;\n        _view = new FormView(metadata);\n        _model = new DataModel(metadata);\n    }\n    \n    public string FormId => _metadata.Id;\n    public FormMetadata Metadata => _metadata;\n    public IFormView View => _view;\n    public IDataModel Model => _model;\n    \n    public void RegisterPlugin(FormPluginBase plugin)\n    {\n        plugin.SetContext(_view, _model);\n        _plugins.Add(plugin);\n    }\n    \n    public async Task OnAfterBindDataAsync()\n    {\n        var e = new AfterBindDataEvent { Data = _model.GetDataEntity() };\n        foreach (var plugin in _plugins)\n        {\n            plugin.OnAfterBindData(e);\n        }\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task OnBeforeOperationAsync(string operationKey)\n    {\n        var e = new BeforeOperationEvent { OperationKey = operationKey };\n        foreach (var plugin in _plugins)\n        {\n            plugin.OnBeforeOperation(e);\n            if (e.Cancel)\n            {\n                throw new OperationCanceledException(e.CancelMessage ?? \"操作被取消\");\n            }\n        }\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task OnAfterOperationAsync(string operationKey)\n    {\n        var e = new AfterOperationEvent { OperationKey = operationKey, Success = true };\n        foreach (var plugin in _plugins)\n        {\n            plugin.OnAfterOperation(e);\n        }\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n}\n\npublic class FormNotFoundException : Exception\n{\n    public FormNotFoundException(string message) : base(message) { }\n}\n\npublic interface IMetadataRepository\n{\n    Task<FormMetadata?> GetFormMetadataAsync(string formId);\n    Task<DynamicObject> LoadDataAsync(string formId, string dataId);\n    Task SaveDataAsync(string formId, DynamicObject data);\n}\n\npublic interface IPluginManager\n{\n    Task<T?> LoadPluginAsync<T>(string pluginId) where T : class, IPlugin;\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227303981}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9f505ee","parentId":"421ff70c","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:03.996Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3699aef649de45afb5c19394","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 金蝶云苍穹前端开发文档\n\n**版本**: 金蝶云苍穹 v8.x  \n**文档ID**: JJC-20260320-001  \n**创建时间**: 2026-03-20\n\n---\n\n## 📋 概述\n\n金蝶云苍穹提供现代化的前端开发框架，支持React、Vue、Angular等多种技术栈，提供丰富的UI组件库和开发工具。\n\n## 🎨 技术栈\n\n### 1. UI框架\n\n| 框架 | 版本 | 推荐场景 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **React** | 18+ | 复杂交互应用 |\n| **Vue.js** | 3.x | 快速开发，中小型应用 |\n| **Angular** | 14+ | 企业级大型应用 |\n\n### 2. 状态管理\n\n| 状态库 | 推荐场景 | 说明 |\n|--------|---------|------|\n| **Redux Toolkit** | React复杂应用 | 可预测状态管理 |\n| **Zustand** | React/Vue快速开发 | 轻量级，API简洁 |\n| **Vuex** | Vue.js应用 | 官方状态管理 |\n| **NgRx** | Angular应用 | 响应式编程 |\n\n### 3. 组件库\n\n**K3Cloud UI Components**（React）:\n```jsx\nimport React from 'react';\nimport { \n  Button, \n  Input, \n  Form, \n  Table, \n  DatePicker, \n  Select,\n  Card,\n  Modal\n} from 'k3cloud-ui';\n\nconst CustomBillForm = () => {\n  const [form, setForm] = React.useState({\n    billNo: '',\n    billDate: null,\n    status: 'draft',\n    remarks: ''\n  });\n\n  const handleSubmit = async (e) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    \n    // 表单验证\n    if (!form.billNo) {\n      alert('单据编号不能为空');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    try {\n      // API调用\n      const response = await api.createBill(form);\n      \n      if (response.success) {\n        alert('单据创建成功');\n        setForm({\n          billNo: '',\n          billDate: null,\n          status: 'draft',\n          remarks: ''\n        });\n      } else {\n        alert(`创建失败: ${response.message}`);\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      console.error('创建失败:', error);\n      alert('系统错误，请稍后重试');\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <Card title=\"自定义单据\">\n      <Form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\n        <Form.Item label=\"单据编号\" required>\n          <Input \n            value={form.billNo}\n            onChange={(e) => setForm({...form, billNo: e.target.value})}\n            placeholder=\"请输入单据编号\"\n            maxLength={50}\n          />\n        </Form.Item>\n\n        <Form.Item label=\"单据日期\" required>\n          <DatePicker \n            value={form.billDate}\n            onChange={(date) => setForm({...form, billDate: date})}\n            placeholder=\"请选择日期\"\n            format=\"YYYY-MM-DD\"\n          />\n        </Form.Item>\n\n        <Form.Item label=\"状态\">\n          <Select \n            value={form.status}\n            onChange={(value) => setForm({...form, status: value})}\n            placeholder=\"请选择状态\"\n            options={[\n              { label: '草稿', value: 'draft' },\n              { label: '已提交', value: 'submitted' },\n              { label: '已审批', value: 'approved' },\n              { label: '已驳回', value: 'rejected' }\n            ]}\n          />\n        </Form.Item>\n\n        <Form.Item label=\"备注\">\n          <Input.TextArea \n            value={form.remarks}\n            onChange={(e) => setForm({...form, remarks: e.target.value})}\n            placeholder=\"请输入备注\"\n            rows={3}\n            maxLength={500}\n          />\n        </Form.Item>\n\n        <Form.Item>\n          <Button type=\"primary\" htmlType=\"submit\">\n            提交\n          </Button>\n          <Button type=\"default\">\n            重置\n          </Button>\n        </Form.Item>\n      </Form>\n    </Card>\n  );\n};\n\nexport default CustomBillForm;\n```\n\n**K3Cloud UI Components**（Vue）:\n```vue\n<template>\n  <k-card title=\"自定义单据\">\n    <k-form @submit=\"handleSubmit\">\n      <k-form-item label=\"单据编号\" required>\n        <k-input \n          v-model=\"form.billNo\"\n          placeholder=\"请输入单据编号\"\n          :maxlength=\"50\"\n        />\n      </k-form-item>\n\n      <k-form-item label=\"单据日期\" required>\n        <k-date-picker \n          v-model=\"form.billDate\"\n          placeholder=\"请选择日期\"\n          format=\"yyyy-MM-dd\"\n        />\n      </k-form-item>\n\n      <k-form-item label=\"状态\">\n        <k-select \n          v-model=\"form.status\"\n          placeholder=\"请选择状态\"\n          :options=\"statusOptions\"\n        />\n      </k-form-item>\n\n      <k-form-item label=\"备注\">\n        <k-input \n          v-model=\"form.remarks\"\n          type=\"textarea\"\n          placeholder=\"请输入备注\"\n          :rows=\"3\"\n          :maxlength=\"500\"\n        />\n      </k-form-item>\n\n      <k-form-item>\n        <k-button type=\"primary\">提交</k-button>\n        <k-button type=\"default\">重置</k-button>\n      </k-form-item>\n    </k-form>\n  </k-card>\n</template>\n\n<script>\nimport { ref, reactive } from 'vue';\nimport { createBill } from '@/api/bill';\n\nexport default {\n  name: 'CustomBillForm',\n  setup() {\n\n[618 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227303990}}
